Havana - Cuba 2001
Photography by Aaron Sosa

A group of workers wait for the "Guagua" public transportation to go home after work.

Aaron Sosa is a photographer and visual artist currently living in Montevideo, Uruguay, where he works for agencies, international editorials and corporate clients. His work has been exhibited in over 110 galleries worldwide and his photographs have been published in journals, books and magazines at an international level.

www.aaronsosaphotography.com
